WEBVTT

1
01:00:57.800 --> 01:00:59.080 
当树木连成森林
And when the forest would grow

2
01:00:59.080 --> 01:01:01.750 
而新生命又无处安放的时候
rank and in need of clearing for new growth...

3
01:01:02.690 --> 01:01:06.240 
我将会点燃这场大火
I was there to set it ablaze.

4
01:01:07.540 --> 01:01:08.680 
那个时候你在哪
Where were you?

5
01:01:09.150 --> 01:01:12.120 
我父母在这里遇害时你在哪
When my father and mother were slaughtered in this place?

6
01:01:12.130 --> 01:01:13.060 
沉睡着
Asleep.

7
01:01:13.500 --> 01:01:15.750 
被困在黑暗中
Trapped in darkness.

8
01:01:16.060 --> 01:01:18.060 
我那时缺席了  我的孩子
I was not there for you, my son.

9
01:01:18.060 --> 01:01:20.440 
可现在我来了
But I am here now.

10
01:01:20.750 --> 01:01:23.540 
你不了解你拥有的力量  但我知道
You don't know your own strength, but I do.

11
01:01:27.520 --> 01:01:29.760 
靠近地面
Reach down.

